---
title: Pumpkin Fusilli & Sage-Walnut Crumb with Pear & Rocket Salad
description: The star of this pasta night is the moreish creamy sauce, with roasted butternut pumpkin stirred through, it’ll melt in your mouth upon
first bite. Topped off with a walnut crumb, your senses will be in for a very special treat
